Geeta Dhami, Trustee Founder of Seva Sankalp Foundation.During the meeting, Smt. Geeta Dhami extended an invitation to the Governor to attend the “Dehradun Uttarayani Kauthik Mahotsav–2026”, being organized under the aegis of the Seva Sankalp Foundation from 05 to 08 February, 2026..……0…….

Lok Bhavan Uttarakhand-Information WingPress Note

Lok Bhavan Dehradun 29 January, 2026

The Hon’ble Governor of Uttarakhand, Lieutenant General Gurmit Singh (Retd.), was paid a courtesy visit today at Lok Bhavan by Smt. Geeta Dhami, Trustee Founder of Seva Sankalp Foundation.

During the meeting, Smt. Geeta Dhami extended an invitation to the Governor to attend the “Dehradun Uttarayani Kauthik Mahotsav–2026”, being organized under the aegis of the Seva Sankalp Foundation from 05 to 08 February, 2026.
